dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: nawaha Khan Bani Sa'd wa Daltawah was Sumaykah
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat al-Misahah al-Ammah. Iraq. Directorate General of Surveys. [[Map of Iraq]: Khan Bani Sa'd, Daltawah, and Sumaykah sections]. Alternate title: Liwa'ay Dayali wa Baghdad: qada'ay Samarra wa Daltawah: nawaha Khan Bani Sa'd wa Daltawah wa Sumaykah. [Dayala and Baghdad provinces: Samarra and Daltawah districts: Khan Bani Sa'd, Daltawah, and Sumaykah sections.] Relief shown by hachures and form lines. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1934. Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
